| **Mar 1 (Sun)**  | **SM i MTBO Uppsala**            | FB + IG  | Championship focus. Terrain description.       |
| **Mar 8 (Sun)**  | **Framtidens Program #2**        | FB       | Strategy deep dive.                            |
| **Mar 15 (Sun)** | **Framtidens Program #3**        | FB       | Karlskrona example.                            |
